name: Blessing
description:
Forgiveness is a right for everyone, everyone has the right to receive it.
arrogance is one of the qualities that exist in every human being, 
arrogance is also what makes people hurt, but if there is not even a little of that feeling, 
it may be that the passion for survival has faded. Therefore, balance is also needed. 
Don't be too arrogant and just highlight your abilities.
